	<summary>A web app for reading the Bible with full emphasis on the God`s Word only. Sola scriptura</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			Read the Bible with full emphasis on God's Word only. Sola scriptura. Read God's Word with a deep understanding of His design. Bible elevates your soul with rapid ascending to calm, safety and more.
		</p>
		<p>
			This app is built for reading the Bible on full screen. There is available such features as Bible texts of 28 translations, search, something like bookmarks, reading history, night/light theme, regulation of font size, font-family and some other small nice features. Localization for **Українська**, **Русский**, **Portuguese** and **Español**.
		</p>
		<p>
			The list of available translations:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>YLT, Young's Literal Translation (1898)</li>
			<li>KJV, King James Version (1769)</li>
			<li>WEB, World English Bible</li>
			<li>RSV, Revised Standard Version (1952)</li>
			<li>CJB, The Complete Jewish Bible (1998)</li>
			<li>NASB, New American Standard Bible (1995)</li>
			<li>GNV, Geneva Bible (1599)</li>
			<li>WLC, Westminster Leningrad Codex (with Vowels)</li>
			<li>WLCC, Westminster Leningrad Codex (Consonants)</li>
			<li>UBIO, Біблія, Іван Іванович Огієнко 1962</li>
			<li>UKRK, Біблія. Пантелеймон Александрович Куліш, Іван Семенович Нечуй-Левицький, Іван Павлович Пулюй,1903</li>
			<li>HOM, Святе Письмо, Переклад Івана Хоменка, 1963</li>
			<li>NRT, Новый Русский Перевод (НРП)</li>
			<li>SYNOD, Русский Синодальный Перевод</li>
			<li>JNT, Еврейский Новый Завет в переводе и комментариях Давида Стерна</li>
			<li>LXX, LXX [A], Accentedq</li>
			<li>NTGT, Greek NT: Tischendorf 8th Ed.</li>
			<li>TR, Elzevir Textus Receptus (1624)</li>
			<li>VULG, Biblia Sacra juxta Vulgatam Clementinam</li>
			<li>CUV, Chinese: Union (Traditional)</li>
			<li>ARA, Almeida Revista e Atualizada, 1959</li>
			<li>NRT, Новый Русский Перевод (НРП)</li>
			<li>MB, Menge-Bibel</li>
			<li>ELB, Elberfelder Bibel, 1871</li>
			<li>LUT, Luther (1912)</li>
			<li>SCH, Schlachter (1951)</li>
			<li>DNB, Det Norsk Bibelselskap (1930)</li>
			<li>BG, Biblia gdańska, 1881</li>
			<li>BW, Biblia warszawska, 1975</li>
			<li>BTX3, La Biblia Textual 3ra Edicion</li>
			<li>RV1960, Reina-Valera 1960</li>
			<li>RV2004, Reina Valera Gómez 2004</li>
			<li>PDT, Palabra de Dios para Todos</li>
			<li>NVI, Nueva Versión Internacional</li>
		</ul>
